<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l22">wıe der <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>leẅt<ex>en</ex></expan> das Jr <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> das daʒ ſıe Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l23"><expan>vorgeſtande<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein als er mıt recht auf ſıe bracht hab etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l24">wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd laſſen eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l25"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu red geſecʒt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> . was er getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l26">hab . hoff er er hab recht daran getan . vvıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l27">Jn daran geweıſet / daʒ er dıe pfand alſo <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>endert</expan> ſol <expan>beleıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_51_r1l28">laſſen / Vnd deẅht eẅch daʒ Jr <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu Jm ıht <expan>ʒeſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett ſo </ab>
