<ab facs="#facs_52_r1l3">mıt dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> niht args ʒe <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb </ab>
