<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hans, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>Seicze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Gewd<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie der <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lewt<ex>en</ex></expan> das ir <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab
                                <expan>üb<ex>er</ex></expan> das, daz sie im
                                <expan>vorgestande<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, als er mit recht auf sie
                        bracht hab etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und lassen ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu red geseczt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>;
                        der hat uns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, was er getan hab, hoff er, er
                        hab recht daran getan. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in daran geweiset, daz er die
                        pfand also <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>endert</expan> sol
                            <expan>beleibe<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen, und dewht ewch, daz ir
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu im iht <expan>ze
                            sprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        ewch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinpott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gewalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> von im <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en,</ex></expan> wenn wir des ermant
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, <pb facs="#facs_52" id="26r"/>so der
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> anheim ist, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Und getrawn ewch wol, ir habt
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> mit dem
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> niht args ze <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ewch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. Und lat uns
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
